Package: buoyant
Type: Package
Title: Deploy '_server.yml' Compliant Applications
Version: 0.1.0
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Authors@R: c(
  person("Barret", "Schloerke", role = c("cre", "aut"), email = "barret@posit.co"))
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.0)
Description: Provides tools to deploy R web server applications that follow
    the '_server.yml' standard. This standard allows different R server
    frameworks (plumber2, fiery, etc.) to be deployed using a common interface.
    The package supports deployment to DigitalOcean and includes validation
    tools to ensure '_server.yml' files are correctly formatted.
